## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ§± **Semantic HTML5 Structure**
- Clean and structured `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`
- SEO-friendly & accessibility-friendly markup
- ARIA labels for navigation

### ğŸ¨ **Modular CSS Architecture**
- `variables.css` â†’ Color palette, fonts, theme settings  
- `style.css` â†’ Main layout & component styles  
- `responsive.css` â†’ Media queries for all devices  

### ğŸ“± **Fully Responsive Design**
- Mobile-first design system
- Flexbox and CSS Grid layouts
- Modern hamburger menu for mobile

### ğŸ§  **Interactive JavaScript**
- Mobile navigation toggle  
- Contact form validation (simulated submit)  
- Auto-updating footer year  

### ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ¦½ **Accessibility**
- Skip-to-content link  
- High contrast colors  
- Semantic labels for screen readers  

